    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, crumble half <span class=\"text-danger\">[all]</span> the<strong> blue cheese</strong> into a bowl with the&nbsp;<strong>white wine vinegar</strong> and mash together to form a rough paste&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> (don't like raw garlic? Go easy!), <strong>mayonnaise</strong> and 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>milk</strong></p>\r\n<p>Season generously with<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up -&nbsp;this is your&nbsp;<strong>blue cheese dressing</strong></p>",
