      "instruction": "<p>Tear the<strong> little gems</strong> into rough bite-sized pieces</p>\r\n<p>Chop the <strong>baby plum tomatoes</strong> in half</p>\r\n<p>Divide the <strong>little gem</strong> and<strong> chopped baby plum tomatoes</strong> between 2<span class=\"text-danger\"> [4]</span> large shallow bowls or plates&nbsp;</p>",
